data.title: Best Western Macrander Hotel Frankfurt/Kaiserlei, Offenbach am Main
data.meta_description: Located in Offenbach am Main in Germany, the family-friendly Best Western Macrander Hotel Frankfurt/Kaiserlei has everything you need for a comfortable stay. Tap on the link to discover more info.
data.text:
About the hotel

A restaurant, a fitness center, and a bar/lounge are available at this smoke-free hotel. WiFi in public areas is free. Additionally, a snack bar/deli, a sauna, and a 24-hour business center are onsite.

Nearby attractions

Best Western Macrander Hotel Frankfurt/Kaiserlei is located in Kaiserlei, a neighborhood in Offenbach am Main, and is in the suburbs and on a river. German Leather Museum and Capitol are cultural highlights, and some of the area's notable landmarks include Buesing Palais and Isenburg Palace. Frankfurt Zoological Garden and Palmengarten are also worth visiting.
